### Create a new Order
POST http://localhost:8081/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": 1,
      "quantity": 2,
      "price": 1200.00
    }
  ],
  "totalAmount": 2400.00
}

### Get Order by ID
GET http://localhost:8081/api/orders/1
Accept: application/json

### Cancel Order
PUT http://localhost:8081/api/orders/1/cancel
Content-Type: application/json

### Payment Callback
POST http://localhost:8081/api/orders/1/payment-callback
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "success": true,
  "transactionId": "txn_123456789"
}